 
  
  <h2>EXPOZINE 2007, MONTREAL&rsquo;S SIXTH ANNUAL SMALL PRESS, COMIC AND ZINE FAIR!</h2>
  <p>Thanks to the <a href="2007.php">exhibitors</a> of all kinds, to our <a href="#sponsors">sponsors</a>, and to the many thousands of visitors and small-press aficionados, we can confidently claim that Expozine 2007 was a huge success! This was the first year that the event was held for two days instead of one, and already, people are clamouring for an even bigger event next year!</p>
  <p>The organizing team:</p>

  <p>Pascal-Angelo Fioramore, Billy Mavreas, Andr&eacute; Racette, Louis Rastelli, Claudine Vachon, and our organizers-emeritus: Andy Brown, Marie-Christine Demers, Ian Ferrier, David Widgington.</p>

  <p>Expozine is organized by ARCMTL, a non-profit organization helping to promote, distribute and preserve independent culture in Montreal.</p>

