  <p>Expozine, Montreal&rsquo;s annual small press, comic and zine fair, took place on Saturday, November 24 and Sunday, November 25, 2007, from 12 p.m. to 6 p.m. at 5035 St-Dominique (&Eacute;glise Saint-Enfant J&eacute;sus, between St-Joseph and Laurier, near Laurier M&eacute;tro) <a href="http://local.google.com/local?f=q&hl=en&q=5035+St-Dominique,+montreal,+quebec,+canada&ie=UTF8&z=15&om=1&iwloc=A" target="_blank">MAP</a>. Free admission.</p>
